Scott,

The whole wiring diagram for your bus is at:

http://www.vintagebus.com/wiring/bus-77-78.jpg

Go there, download it or at least look at it.  Everywhere you see an "S"
with a number beside it...  those are your fuses and the number indicates
position in the fuse box.

